Class FragmentReviewLocations

  • java.lang.Object
    • Fragment
      • com.chdryra.android.mygenerallibrary.FragmentDeleteDone
        • com.chdryra.android.reviewer.FragmentReviewGrid<T>
          • com.chdryra.android.reviewer.FragmentReviewGridAddEditDone<GVLocationList.GVLocation>
            • com.chdryra.android.reviewer.FragmentReviewLocations 

  • public class FragmentReviewLocations
extends FragmentReviewGridAddEditDone<GVLocationList.GVLocation>
    UI Fragment: review locations. Each grid cell shows a location name.

    FragmentReviewGrid functionality:

    • Subject: disabled
    • RatingBar: disabled
    • Banner button: launches ActivityReviewLocationMap showing current location
    • Grid cell click: launches ActivityReviewLocationMap showing clicked location
    • Grid cell long click: same as click

    See Also:
    ActivityReviewLocations, ActivityReviewLocationMap
